# TesNet — Production installation guide

> **Start here for a full walkthrough (factory-reset ProBook + MikroTik):**  
> **[`docs/PROBOOK_MIKROTIK_FULL_SETUP.md`](docs/PROBOOK_MIKROTIK_FULL_SETUP.md)** — step-by-step from zero, including `http-pap`, certificates/HTTPS, power-off & reboot recovery, leak tests, and troubleshooting.

This guide covers a **fresh Ubuntu Server** install on an **HP ProBook** (billing + RADIUS + database) and **MikroTik hAP²** (hotspot + Wi‑Fi) for the TesNet student ISP stack.

For Paystack HTTPS/webhooks and hotspot HTML details, also read:

- [`docs/HOTSPOT.md`](docs/HOTSPOT.md)
- [`docs/PAYSTACK.md`](docs/PAYSTACK.md)

