## 8. Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Check |
|---------|--------|
| Free internet before Connect | §5.7: remove broad walled-garden rules; disable trial; remove `ip-binding bypassed`; check firewall forward rules |
| Portal not loading on phone | Walled garden; DNS; `APP_URL` reachable from Wi‑Fi |
| RADIUS reject | `radius.log`, secret match, username = phone `233…` in `radcheck` |
| Login OK but no internet | Hotspot authorized; NAT rule; upstream WAN |
| Paystack works but no data | Webhook HTTPS; `transactions.status=success`; `package_purchases` row |
| Wrong speed/data cap | `radreply` rows; reconnect Wi‑Fi after purchase |
| FreeRADIUS won’t start | `freeradius -CX`; SQL password; `mods-enabled/sql` |

Useful commands:

```bash
# Ubuntu
